{"tid":1844062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林鄭滅國】工信部：正尋求海外採購口罩防護服等裝備","createTime":"2020-01-26T12:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T13:38:01.000Z","uid":152636,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"511ec70a3ed321ab8ff22a822f35bbbc47dca836","tid":1844062,"uid":152636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在北京，國家衞生健康委員會表示，從臨床的經驗顯示新型冠狀病毒傳播力有所增強，對防疫構成一定壓力。<span style=\"color: red;\">而工業和信息化部承認全國防護服的生產力未能滿足湖北省的需求。</span><br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診個案不斷上升，中央多個部委開記者會交代最新防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n國家衞健委表示，春節假期是遏制武漢以外疫情蔓延的關鍵時期，是隔離、消毒措施發揮作用的最佳時間。<br />\n<br />\n他們承認最新的臨床證據顯示，病毒人與人傳播力增強，對防疫構成一定的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陸續有捐贈物資包括防護服、消毒液等由全國各地送到湖北省，統一發放到全省各地的醫療機構。<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據湖北省的需求清單，每天需要防護服十萬件，他們承認全國的產能未能滿足武漢的需求。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示會使用中央儲備之外，亦正尋求在海外採購口罩、防護服等裝備。<br />\n<br />\n差不多所有出席記者會的人都戴口罩，國務院新聞辦公室一改以往作風，沒有要求我們除下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7婆一方面要向國務院拎口罩，但另一邊根本自己都唔夠用，7婆仲唔係想滅國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f77872746d17801d518b1e79ee530c19e4db99c3","tid":1844062,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"叫國務院支援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c52daed36a7b15e083f63be4ff45019204cebd7","tid":1844062,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"咁先未滿足到一個省嘅消耗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b2de4d38a8b33fe70a797f21ec72595aa792a4","tid":1844062,"uid":76591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"一陣就鬧人地境外勢力，轉個頭又尋求國際幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e6786c1a908da34cf8811e04e239d009326f61","tid":1844062,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地都問外國拎"},{"pid":"9c0f21d6e4a61972cf537834e747d89741fa71d0","tid":1844062,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cb513e37ef021d67e44fc6969fc720113c23ae","tid":1844062,"uid":103050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"中共不嬲講左等於做左，最後實際向香港提供負一億個口罩"},{"pid":"be829fce251c603b7ec300e1cb7ffa26e780dee1","tid":1844062,"uid":198829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"出埋聲要同外國買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7e2eb16dd7d3cd5969f4e39098235f68eba144","tid":1844062,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77872746d17801d518b1e79ee530c19e4db99c3","tid":1844062,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"叫國務院支援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"支那到時會話全中國都唔夠用但係比左香港用先"},{"pid":"e4122a45154b24b8594e3b76d93c71eecea8eb13","tid":1844062,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"7b3fc03d0eab87fe76dae4c3d266098926af2c54","tid":1844062,"uid":19278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"2000億同美帝買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675782ec3a09cdaca0223146e2398ce4c9db9e01","